${
  $d R q r s t u v w x y z $. $d S q r s t u v w x y z $.
  $d X q r s t u v w x y z $. $d Y q r s t u v w x y z $.
  $d A q r s t u v w x y z $. $d B q r s t u v w x y z $.
  txsubsp.1 $e |- X = U. R $.
  txsubsp.2 $e |- Y = U. S $.
  $( The subspace of a topological product space induced by a subset with
  a Cartesian product representation is a topological product of the
  subspaces induced by the subspaces of the terms of the products. $)
  txsubsp $p |- ( ( ( R e. Top /\ S e. Top ) /\ ( A (_ X /\ B (_ Y ) ) ->
                    ( subSp ` <. ( A X. B ) , ( R tX S ) >. ) =
